short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Deliverr's browser extension for managing eBay Guaranteed Delivery rate tables.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Deliverr's browser extension that creates surcharge rate tables on eBay with the click of a button. Required for enabling Fast Shipping estimates and badges on eBay listings for sellers using Deliverr for fulfillment.
